BASEBALL

BOSTON (AL) - Activated Steve Crawford, pitcher, from the 15-day disabled list. Placed Dennis (Oil Can) Boyd, pitcher, on the 15-day disabled list.

CINCINNATI (NL) - Purchased contract of Jeff Montgomery, pitcher, from Nashville of the American Association. Sent Bill Landrum, pitcher, outright to Nashville.

HOUSTON (NL) - Placed Jim Deshaies, pitcher, on the 15-day disabled list. Purchased the contract of Jeff Heathcock, pitcher, from Tucson of the Pacific Coast League.

CLEVELAND (AL) - Traded Steve Carlton, pitcher, to the Minnesota Twins for a player to be named. Recalled Jeff Kaiser, pitcher, from Buffalo of the American Association.